Description: Time-Weighted Spatial Averaging (TWSA) methods for calculating activity space and environmental exposure from GPS data.
  This package implements four TWSA methods - Point Overlay, Kernel Density Estimation, Density Ranking 
  (Jankowska et al., 2023 <doi.org/10.1016/j.healthplace.2021.102706>)
  with the addtion of Line Segment method (github.com/michaeldgarber/microclim-static-v-dynam). 
